The BEST (and ONLY) source URL File Explorer for the web! Save thousands of files and hundreds of gigabytes using this software. The internet is now YOURS for the taking!!! So what are you waiting for — TAKE IT :)

This extension allows a user to locate any video or image on the web that he/she wishes to save as a bookmark, lets them save the url/link (as opposed to the video or image file itself), and subsequently store and export/download their url collection(s).
